{"3993630": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Femboy Detective", "steam_appid": 3993630, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/37c1f9398ceb97a2f25048400fd77dec.poster.avif?t=1765332329\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/37c1f9398ceb97a2f25048400fd77dec.webm?t=1765332329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/37c1f9398ceb97a2f25048400fd77dec.mp4?t=1765332329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With summer break right around the corner, Jay thought this was his chance to confess to his crush. She listened while he poured his heart out and, finally, asked for time to think.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The next day, she vanished.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to find her.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/231123b8a96a784f74b2e5491de5559c.poster.avif?t=1765332329\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/231123b8a96a784f74b2e5491de5559c.webm?t=1765332329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/231123b8a96a784f74b2e5491de5559c.mp4?t=1765332329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/15c1a7f970b29bc05db0d0352a6914fa.avif?t=1765332329\" width=241 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our protagonist. A sophomore at Sturgeon Academy. An amateur detective, thrust into the role by the sudden disappearance of his friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/ba1a53560ea1f6e19c628f95ae1a990d.avif?t=1765332329\" width=241 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jay didn't meet Robin until a week after he was declared missing. He's seen him around town, always watching...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>He says Aveline is trapped in an underground bunker.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/11f07c561e3cbf7f165b4b90fb1cb175.avif?t=1765332329\" width=241 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In spite of his appearance, Night is an upperclassman. For some reason he despises Jay and has decided to make that his problem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>He says Aveline did something unforgivable.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/c52eb4bd3eae1d60bba51631fc741c3b.avif?t=1765332329\" width=241 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jay's best friend. Things have been tense between them since Aveline came into the picture- Jay suspects that he has a crush on her too. Though her disappearance didn't seem to bother him...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>He says you should stop looking for answers.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3993630/extras/4b77aa6ac54202204348ec9b445eaa59.poster.avif?t=1765332329\" wid